---
title: 'Streamlined access management experience'
summary: 'Manage access grants and custom roles faster with our simplified user interface.'
releaseDate: '2025-12-09'
learnMoreLink: 'https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/accounts/accounts-billing/new-relic-one-user-management/user-management-concepts/#understand-concepts'
